<div class="artwork-content">

        <div id="artwork-image">
            <a href="..\/images\/286027_4265665.jpg" class="enlargement-link enlargement-link-87643"><img src="images/286027_4265667.jpg" alt="The Two Disciples at the Tomb" title="Henry Ossawa Tanner
