    <p class="tools">
              <a href="..\/images\/286027_4265665.jpg" class="enlargement-link enlargement-link-87643"><strong>View</strong> enlargement</a><br />
                          <a href="http://www.artic.edu/aic/collections/exhibitions/AfricanAmerican/artwork/87643/email"><strong>Email</strong> to a friend</a><br />
